Class Electronic

  • java.lang.Object
    • Items
      • Electronic
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Computer, SmartPhone, Tv

    public abstract class Electronic
extends Items
    The Electronic abstract class has features which every electronic product has.This abstract class has abstract methods which are no need to be implemented in this class.

    Muhammet Selcuk Guvel
